# Deep-Sea Marine Research Vessel Technical Dashboard

## Top Bar
- Vessel Name: **RV ABYSSAL EXPLORER**
- Depth: **___ m**
- Coordinates: **___° ___' N, ___° ___' E**
- Mission Timer: **___ hrs**
- Connectivity Indicators:
  - Satellite 📡 (Status: ___)
  - Acoustic Modem 🎚️ (Status: ___)
  - ROV Tether 🎮 (Status: ___)

## Left Panel – Navigation & Sonar
- **Multibeam Sonar** (scrolling waterfall)
- **Side‑Scan Sonar** (Port / Starboard)
- **Sub‑Bottom Profiler**
- **Current Position** on Bathymetric Map (with waypoints)
- **Heading**, **SOG**, **Speed Through Water**

## Center Panel – ROV/AUV Control
- **Live Video Feed** (Main Camera / Manipulator Cam)
- **ROV Telemetry**:
  - Depth, Heading, Altitude, Tether Tension
  - Thruster Status (4‑Thruster Layout)
- **Manipulator Arm** (7‑DOF)
  - Gripper Force Feedback
- **Tool Skid** (Samplers, Sensors, Corers)
- **Auto‑Station Keeping / DP** status

## Right Panel – Environmental & Science
- **CTD Profile** (real‑time graph)
- **Dissolved O₂, pH, Turbidity, Methane**
- **Water Column Backscatter**
- **Sample Log**:
  - Niskin Bottles, Push Cores, Bioboxes, Rock Boxes, eDNA Sampler
- **Sensor Readings** (temp, salinity, pressure)

## Bottom Panel – Systems Monitoring
- **Power Distribution** (Main Bus, Battery SOC, Generator)
- **Propulsion** (Azimuth Thrusters RPM, Tunnel Thrusters)
- **Ballast & Trim** (Tank Levels, Trim Angle)
- **Communications** (VSAT, Acoustic SNR, UHF/VHF)
- **Life Support** (O₂, CO₂, Hull Integrity)
- **Alarm Banner** (Red/Amber/Green status)

## Styling
- **Theme:** Dark bridge (#0a0f1a) with cyan/teal accents, amber warnings, red criticals, green normals.
- **Fonts:** Monospace for numeric data; technical grid lines; subtle glow on active elements.
- **Contrast:** Optimized for low‑light bridge conditions.
